{"tid":1812304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔擔心武漢肺炎】陳浩民識得自我保護 唔會避到大陸工作","createTime":"2020-01-05T11:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T00:47:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9da0438c13fc6b14cac5a0418d72ac2af58fbc44","tid":1812304,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"陳浩民夫婦與3女1仔，今日到荃灣出席活動，4位小孩十分活躍，更即場表演空中跳舞。近日武漢不明肺炎個案急增，常在大陸拍戲的陳浩民暫時不用到大陸工作，將會留港度歲的他表示不擔心情況，也不會避到大陸的工作：「一直都有注重衛生，自我保護，宜家有新情況就做多少少，唔使太緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n陳浩民指平日專注工作，湊小孩任務主要由太太蔣麗莎負責，他感激太太付出：「好彩有太太幫，佢真係好唔話得，捱咗四刀，養好簡單，食兩碗飯，但育兒先最困難。」他笑言不敢自己湊細路：「一個帶4個好快光頭，我啲頭髮冇乜剩。」至於會否再追多一個仔，他表示生幾多天註定，順其自然就好。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩民笑言自己是家中最活躍的孩子，不過太太就覺得6歲兒子陳璟逸最活躍，但3個女兒不會常跟他玩，令自己要多花時間與他溝通。問到陳浩民孩子中最錫是誰？他就強調個個一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200105/large/1578216290_4715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200105%2Flarge%2F1578216290_4715.jpg&h=1ef350f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200105/large/1578216287_f336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200105%2Flarge%2F1578216287_f336.jpg&h=77cf5c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200105/60453124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200105%2F60453124&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1ZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=53c31c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200105%2F60453124&h=3c71c2f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200105/60453124</a>"},{"pid":"ce876615d457e2f5b07173128fca81901127e0ae","tid":1812304,"uid":119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep